name: magical grid
description:
In celebration of the 20th anniversary of Processing.

Discs are pulsating at constant but slightly shifted frequencies, creating innumerable continuously morphing patterns.

0 to start over
6 to speed up
4 to slow down
9 to enlarge the dots
7 to shrink the dots
2 to invert b&w
1 to stop/start again

interactive sketch | p5js | @wavegrower
